Consent Management
We participate in IAB Europe's transparency and consent framework and comply with its specifications and guidelines. To this end, we use the Consent Management Platform (CMP) from InMobi as a subcontractor. In accordance with the IAB Europe Transparency and Consent Framework, InMobi is identified as IAB Europe ID #10. InMobi's CMP allows you to grant us data protection compliant consent to process your data and to revoke such consent at any time. You may also object to the processing of data based on our legitimate interest.
